                "type": "Paragraph",
                "data": {
                  "inline": [
                    {
                      "type": "Words",
                      "data": {
                        "value": "Jacobian matrix of the right-hand side of the system with respect to y, required by this method. The Jacobian matrix has shape (n, n) and its element (i, j) is equal to "
