                      "wh": {
                        "_lines": []
                      },
                      "ind": {
                        "_lines": [
                          {
                            "_line": "      t and y; it will be called as ``jac(t, y)`` as necessary.",
                            "_number": 8,
                            "_offset": 6
                          },
                          {
                            "_line": "      For the 'Radau' and 'BDF' methods, the return value might be a",
                            "_number": 9,
